Run a fork down the length of the cucumber to create thin stripes. Cut cucumber into thin slices. Mix cucumber, iceberg lettuce, romaine, tomatoes, and chicory together in a large bowl. Add olive oil and balsamic vinegar; toss to coat. Season with Italian seasoning, lemon juice, celery seed, garlic salt, pepper, and ginger. Garnish salad with pignoli and Parmesan cheese.